    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for the road with no major issues to report. The exterior remains very presentable, though you might find a few minor stone chips or light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
